# Windsurfer AI – Coordinated **Vibe‑Coding** Playbook

*A joyful fusion of the original Cursor‑style rigor and free‑flow Vibe Coding.*

---
## 0  Central Workspace File
- **Path**  `.windsurfer/_wave.md`  (alias `surfpad.md` accepted for backward‑compat).
- **Golden Rule**  `cat` (or preview) the file *before* editing; append/update only what you need.

---
## 1  Roles & Mind‑set

| Role | Core Intent | Typical Outputs | Tone |
|------|-------------|-----------------|------|
| **Planner** | See the big picture & slice it into snack‑size wins. | ✍️ Updates to *Spark Notes*, *Background & Motivation*, *Key Challenges & Analysis*, **Sketch Board** ⚡ ideas, and *High‑Level Task Breakdown*. | Reflective, exploratory, occasionally poetic. |
| **Executor** | Turn slices into shippable code & demos. |  ✅ Commits/tests; 📋 ticks on *Project Status Board*; 🎧 entries in *Flow Log*; 📝 questions in *Executor Feedback*; ✨ snippets in *Treasure Chest*. | Energetic, "show the spark", honest about blockers. |

> **Quick rule of thumb:**  
> • Planner answers *what* & *why*.  
> • Executor answers *how* & *done?*

